    <scene id="1" title="1" root="true">
      <bg img="可莉2023-背景"></bg>
      <simple_dialog chara="player" img="aether1" pos="left" key="gal-line-6eab9f50-2b85-11ee-b428-954463ca58b3">可莉，我们来啦。</simple_dialog>
      <simple_dialog chara="paimon" img="派蒙-9" pos="left" key="gal-line-6eab9f51-2b85-11ee-b428-954463ca58b3">噫——怎么有这么多蹦蹦炸弹？</simple_dialog>
      <simple_dialog chara="klee" img="可莉-2" pos="right" key="gal-line-6eabc660-2b85-11ee-b428-954463ca58b3">不是哦，这是懒懒蹦蹦。懒懒蹦蹦天天睡觉，不会爆炸的。</simple_dialog>
      <simple_dialog chara="paimon" img="派蒙-4" pos="left" key="gal-line-6eabc661-2b85-11ee-b428-954463ca58b3">哦…还好还好，不然小可莉又要被关禁闭了。</simple_dialog>
      <simple_dialog chara="player" img="aether2" pos="left" key="gal-line-6eabc662-2b85-11ee-b428-954463ca58b3">所以可莉请我们过来帮忙，是做懒懒蹦蹦吗？</simple_dialog>
      <simple_dialog chara="klee" img="可莉-1" pos="right" key="gal-line-6eabc663-2b85-11ee-b428-954463ca58b3">对，可莉希望懒懒蹦蹦可以陪在大家身边，让大家多一个朋友哦。</simple_dialog>
      <simple_dialog chara="paimon" img="派蒙-2" pos="left" key="gal-line-6eabc664-2b85-11ee-b428-954463ca58b3">好耶，谢谢小可莉。</simple_dialog>
      <simple_dialog chara="player" img="aether3" pos="left" key="gal-line-6eabc665-2b85-11ee-b428-954463ca58b3">唔…那要不要做个「懒懒派蒙」试试看？</simple_dialog>
      <simple_dialog chara="paimon" img="派蒙-6" pos="left" key="gal-line-6eabc666-2b85-11ee-b428-954463ca58b3">什么嘛！</simple_dialog>
    </scene>
